title: Do I REALLY look like that? (Pictures)
itunes:title: Do I REALLY look like that? (Pictures)
description:
If you're someone who makes excuses about standing in the back or ducking behind a plant when pictures are being taken, then listen in to this podcast.

We'll talk about why looking at pictures is hard and how to get past it.
